<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA37">
<l>āmā ṟaṟivuṭaiyā rāva taritaṉṟē</l>
<l>nāmē yatuvuṭaiyō naṉṉeñcē pūmēy</l>
<l>matukaramē taṇṭuḻāy mālārai vāḻttā</l>
<l>matukaramē yaṉpā lamai.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There being those who posses knowledge of the way it is, is it not rare?</l>
<l>It is us who possess that, good heart. That which is praise of Māl</l>
<l>with cool Tulsi joined by honeymakers that graze on flowers</l>
<l>is [our] duty. Do it with love!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
